name: testCloseBuildPopUpOfFreestyle
description: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Freestyle project build from timeline
descriptionHtml: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Freestyle project build from timeline

testStage.description: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Freestyle project build from timeline

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Verify that build bubble pop up is displayed from timeline
